caption.paragraph:
FIGURE 30.

Ithyphenes rectifrons


sp. nov.

, orig. Holotype, male from MSW (“… Umumgar S.F.…”); 
A
: body, dorsal; 
B
: head, dorsal; 
C
: head and prothorax, ventral; 
D
: terminal abdominal segment, ventral; 
E
male anal sclerite and 
spiculum gastrale
, ventral; 
F
: tegmen, ventral; 
G
: penis trunk, dorsal; 
H
: proximal part of inner sac with armature. Scale bars: 
a
= 1.0 mm to Fig. A; 
b
= 0.5 mm to Figs B–D; 
с
= 0.25 mm to Figs E–H.
